				<div class="comment-body"><p>There are no issues with using the Hugo Awards service marks, if that&#8217;s what you mean. To the best of our knowledge, the only real issue is that no publisher/editor has wanted to take on the somewhat substantial challenge of obtaining the rights to collect the works and the commercial challenge of publishing such a collection.</p>
</div>

