				<div class="comment-body"><p>Katarina:</p>
<p>The Hugo Awards are open to works published in any language, including French. Note that there is no submission process for the Hugo Awards. Works are nominated by the thousands of members of the World Science Fiction Convention. See the <a href="../../index.html?page_id=191">Submissions page</a> for a longer explanation.</p>
</div>

