				<div class="comment-body"><p>The <a href="https://dublin2019.com/whats-on/special-events/special-events-in-the-auditorium/" rel="nofollow">2019 Hugo Awards Ceremony</a> will be hosted by Afua Richardson and Michael Scott.</p>
